Added research request endpoints to topics router. Users can now create research requests linked to topics via POST /api/topics/{id}/requests.

Implementation:
- Added POST /api/topics/{topic_id}/requests endpoint to create research requests linked to topics
- Added GET /api/topics/{topic_id}/requests endpoint to list research requests for a topic
- Research requests automatically get topic_id set when created via topic endpoint
- Supports both project_id and topic_id on research requests for flexible organization

Tests: 21/21 passed (6 new tests covering research request creation and retrieval)
- Verified topic_id is properly set on created requests
- Tested error handling for non-existent topics
- Tested listing requests (empty and with data)
- Tested combination of project_id and topic_id
